Ing '''Piedmont''' metung yang malating karinan da  reng atinan<ref>{{cite web|url=http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/QTTable?_bm=y&-geo_id=16000US0656938&-qr_name=DEC_2000_SF3_U_DP3&-ds_name=DEC_2000_SF3_U&-_lang=en&-_sse=on|title=Piedmont city, California - DP-3. Profile of Selected Economic Characteristics:  2000:|date=September 17, 2008<!-- 1:57:23 AM-->|accessdate=2008-09-17}}</ref> a lakanbalen king [[Alameda County, California|Alameda County]], [[California]],  [[United States]]. Makapadurut ya kareng lakanbalen ning [[Oakland, California|Oakland]]. 10,952 ya ing kayang populasiun [[2000 United States Census|2000 census]]. Ing Piedmont metung ya kareng "25 Matas-Panakitan a Balen" agpang keng CNN Money Magazine's list of 'The Best Places to Live inyang [[2007]] at milagyuan ya naman "Pekamasanting a Karinan a Tuknangnan (Best Place To Live)"  keng United States inyang 2007 agapang keng Forbes.


